						<p>Your name and personal information is protected by The Trophyist</p>
						<br/>
						<p>*Under no circumstances will the fortunate person who received a trophy from suppport@TheTrophyist.com know who sent it unless you give us permission or we are required by law—that means that a person may(slim chance)order a court to subpoena our company.  Yes-we do need to comply with the court system since they trump our confidentially assurance.</p>
						<br/>
						<p>*So that means:  Consider wisely who you send a trophy to as they have the right to take us to court to unearth your identity.</p>  
						<br/>
						<p>*We do not expect this to occur and we have not seen the inside of a courtroom
							 about this.</p>
						<hr/>
						<h3>Credit Card Information</h3>
						<br/>
						<p>*Clearly you will have to purchase the Trophy through support@TheTrophyist.com.</p>
						<br/>
						<p>*So…..you will need to provide a credit card or paypal information with our super secure 3rd party company. </p>
						<br/>
						<p>*The payment processing business that we use is overly (and that’s good) secure.  Support@TheTrophyist.com is a very secure website built by a tremendously brilliant Web Developer.</p>
						<br/>
						<p>*Your personal information is securely protected and we will never sell that  private stuff to any other companies or strangers.  Our Pinky Swear Promise to You!</p>
						<br/>
						<p>*A 3rd party payment software system is used to finalize your unique order.  Please remember to to enable “no cookies” on your phone/computer.</p>
						<br/>
						<hr/>
						<h3>Copyrights</h3>
						<br/>
						<p>The Trophyist is a registered LLC.  This concept has taken countless hours of brainstorming, spats, opinions, trust, love, peace and harmony, and 2 hours of sleep a night in order to bring your this amazing product.  I urge you not to steal the concept, change it up or straight up copy it.</p>
						<br/>
						<p>*The result would be an unpleasant lawsuit and don’t we all just to be 
								honorable, upstanding citizens or tempt bad Karma, Mojo or JuJu?</p>
								<br/>
						<hr/>
						<h3>The Trophyist Cans and Can’ts</h3>
						<br/>
						<p>*What you can do with the The Trophyist?</p>
						<br/>
								<p class="p-l-20">*buy, buy and purchase for friends, family, co-workers, neighbors,
									businesses, bachelorette/bachelor parties, tournaments, games or 
									yourself.</p>
									<br/>
								 
								<p class="p-l-20">*Have a great idea that you would like to see our company offer?
									Email us and we will consider it and award YOU a Trophy for a super            
									dope idea.</p>
									<br/>
						<p>*What you cannot do:</p>
						<br/>
								<p class="p-l-20">*This is a big one so scan carefully(does anyone read word for word 
									anymore?)</p>
									<br/>
								<p class="p-l-20">*Our idea is not original-its been done in some form or another for years.</p>
								<br/>
								<p>*The Trophyist is supposed to funny, sarcastic and a little snarky or
								just plain nice.</p>
								<br/>
										 <p>*Sending it anonymously is part of the fun or sending with your name
											 is just as amusing.</p>
											 <br/>
										 <p>*The Trophyist Teams policy is not intended to bully, stalk, or 
											 threaten anyone.  That just wouldn’t be cricket.</p>
											 <br/>
										 <p>*Our Team will refund your money immediately and we will be 
											 unable to send your gift if the intention is about the above 
											 “Cannot.”</p>
											 <br/>
										 <p>*The Trophyist Team does possess a moral code of conduct and
											 standards.  We retain the right to deny your purchase based
								on certain words. Some words are just not necessary or remotely 
											 acceptable.</p>
											 <br/>
										 <p>*Trust us-we are not prudes, judgmental or prissy but there is a
												limit.  The “C” word will never be used on any trophy or 
												personal note.</p>
												<br/>
			
										 <p>*YOU CAN SEND ONE TO ANYONE ELSE AND MAKE 
												THEIR DAY, MONTH, YEAR AND LIFE BETTER!</p>
